C u s t o m e r   R e v i e w s  >>

Hot..!! 4/5

     
by Provocateur:
"Depeche Mode's great comeback with the second single from their album"Playing the Angel". The Jacques Lu Cont remixes rock the house, while Goldfrapp's soothing version makes this a great chill out track." 


Lu Cont does it again 5/5

     
by TheReflex: 
"This is the year of Lu Cont (AKA Stuart Price). The first track is a real stomper and just when you think it cant get any better the dub comes along and delivers the knockout. Although I'm a big fan of Mode's new release Playing The Angel, Lu Cont's remix takes the song to the next level......You be the judge." 


Orgasmic!! 5/5

     
by L.A.Goddess: 
"I love the Lu Cont Dub version! Makes me dance in my car on the freeway.. Thank goodness for traffic! I highly reccomend this single. In fact I reccomend all Depeche Mode singles. This single, so worth it!"
